{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"957091aa4a","title":"新民学会一次讨论记载――提出无产阶级革命和无产阶级专政的主张","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8fc5f3185a","index":0,"year":1921,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"957091aa4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fa047a9e54","type":"title","text":"新民学会一次讨论记载――提出无产阶级革命和无产阶级专政的主张","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"d42a8f57bd","type":"paragraph","text":"《达到目的须釆用什么方法？》","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"d4411e9602","type":"paragraph","text":"首由毛润之报告巴黎方面蔡和森君的提议。并云：世界解决社会问题的方法大概有下列几种：","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"7b0761e228","type":"paragraph","text":"1．社会政策","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"593e736395","type":"paragraph","text":"2．社会民主主义","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"44b8dbfca0","type":"paragraph","text":"3．激烈方法的共产主义（列宁的主义）","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"9ab5602dee","type":"paragraph","text":"4．温和方法的共产主义（罗素的主义）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"31d3129e48","type":"paragraph","text":"5．无政府主义","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"637af4248f","type":"paragraph","text":"我们可以拿来参考以决定自己的方法。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"3b1f3efbbf","type":"paragraph","text":"何叔衡：主张过激主义，一次的扰乱，抵得二十年的教育，我深信这些。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"},{"id":"040bd0554b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛润之：我的意见与何君大体相同。社会政策，是补苴罅漏的政策，不成办法。社会民主主义，借议会为改造工具，但事实上议会的立法总是保护有产阶级的。无政府主义否认权力，这种主义，恐怕永世都做不到。温和方法的共产主义，如罗素所主张的极端的自由，放任资本家，亦是永世做不到的。急烈方法的共产主义，即所谓劳农主义，用阶级专政的方法，是可以预计效果的。故最宜釆用。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a"}],"page":{"id":"ef9d2a4d38","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"957091aa4a","start":108,"end":109}}}},"__N_SSG":true}